Stops recording.

#### `clear()`

```typescript
clear(): void
```

Clears recorded history and refreshes the initial snapshot if `captureInitialSnapshot` is enabled.

#### `getTickHistory()`

```typescript
getTickHistory(): Array<WorldHistoryTick<TEventMap, TDebug>>
